      "span_text": "To evaluate the drug-release kinetic patterns, drug-release data were assessed using zero order, first order, Higuchi, Korsmeyer and Hixson-Crowell kinetic models. [CITATION_1] Abbreviations: DOX-L, doxorubicin-loaded liposomes; DOX-PeL, Pe-conjugated doxorubicin-loaded liposomes; Pe, phosphatidylethanolamine; sPc, soya-L-α-lecithin; chL, cholesterol; w/w, weight/weight; sD, standard deviation.",
